My Emacs config
===============

Features
--------
  - irony-mode for C, C++ and Objective-C development
  - elpy for Python development
  - emms for a better life (You can listen to Mozart while coding)

Installation
------------
  1. Install Steve Purcell's Emacs configuration:
     git clone git@github.com:purcell/emacs.d.git ~/.emacs.d
  3. Copy the file "init-local.el" to ~/.emacs.d/lisp/
     cp init-local.el ~/.emacs.d/lisp/
